main event: On 29 July 1967, an unidentified flying object was observed crossing the sky from west to east in approximately one minute.
interesting points: The object was described as a white flashing light,The report was filed by personnel at Springfield Municipal Airport,The object was perceived similarly to that of an aircraft,There was no recollection of any aircraft in the area during the observation,The investigation suggests further inquiries may be necessary to identify the object.
